data.description:
Welcome to your new home! This expansive property, located on over half an acre, offers the perfect balance of space and convenience. Situated near schools, shopping centers, and dining options, this home's prime location ensures you'll have easy access to all your daily necessities and entertainment needs.

This 3860 sqft home boasts six generously sized bedrooms, each complete with large walk-in closets, providing ample storage space for all your belongings. With 3.5 baths, there will never be a rush for the bathroom in the mornings. Property is situated on 1/2 acre lot (MOL) and features a half court basketball court, storage shed, and massive concrete patio with enough room for pergola, outdoor kitchen, or hot tub. The possibilities are endless. 

Inside, you'll find two spacious living areas and two dining areas, allowing for both formal and casual gatherings. 

Sellers are highly motivated and have priced this one to sell and allow its new owner to add its own personal touches and updates. Additionally, it comes with several features already in place. The newer windows help to maximize energy efficiency and create a bright and welcoming atmosphere throughout the house, both hot water tanks were replaced in 2019. With both HVAC mechanical systems being replaced in 2021, they also have an extended warranty, giving you peace of mind.

We invite you to schedule a private showing and explore all the potential this property has to offer. Call today to secure your appointment and envision the possibilities of turning this spacious house into your dream home.
